window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ken and company find that with the introduction of the Threadspawn, the whole dungeon becomes far less friendly. Even the populace on Earth is spooked.</p> <p>Which is why the UG and Haylon sends Ken and a few others on the press tour. Though, even that can't keep Ken from the action. The Threadspawn invade Earth—meanwhile Ken is recruited fully into the demon hierarchy.</p> <p>Now he has to balance loyalties to the UG and the Hierachry while the Threadspawn threat grows ever closer.</p>"; 
